name: Greyson_Living_Chester_96-Inch_Dining_Table
description:
The rustic style of the Chester dining table offers a unique style with its saw-horse inspired base. Finished in distressed warm espresso, the dining table comes with two 12-inch leaves that expand the length of the table to a gracious 96 inches.
